casebody.data:
No. 993,

Mise.

In re Disbarment of Lichota.

Edith Fischer Lichota, of Twinsburg, Ohio, having resigned as a member of the Bar of this Court, it is ordered that her name be stricken from the roll of attorneys admitted to practice in this Court. The rule to show cause heretofore issued [ante, p. 812] is discharged.
